@using DTOLayer.Dtos.IncomingGoodsTrackingDtos
@using AquaBusinessTrackingWebUI.Models
@model ModalViewModel<IncomingGoodsTrackingDto>

<div class="modal fade" id="incomingGoodsTrackingModal" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl">
        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">@Model.ModalTitle</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
            </div>

            <form method="post" action="/IncomingGoodsTracking/Edit">

                <div class="modal-body">

                    <input type="hidden" name="IsEdit" value="@Model.IsEdit.ToString().ToLower()" />

                    @if (Model.IsEdit)
                    {
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Entity.RecId" />
                    }

                    <div class="row g-3">

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Tarih</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.ReceiptDate" type="date" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Saat</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.ScaleHours" type="time" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Vardiya</label>
                            <select asp-for="Entity.ShiftId" asp-items="ViewBag.Shifts" class="form-select">
                                <option value="">Vardiya Seçiniz</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Birim</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.Unit" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">İrsaliye No</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.WaybillNo" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">Fiş No</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.ReceiptNo" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">Cari</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.CurrentAccountName" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">Malzeme</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.InventoryName" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">Araç Plakası</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.Plate" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">Operatör</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.Operator" class="form-control" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">İrsaliye Miktarı</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.WaybillQuantity"
                                   class="form-control"
                                   type="number"
                                   step="0.01" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Dolu Ağırlık</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.FilledQuantity"
                                   id="filledQuantity"
                                   class="form-control"
                                   type="number"
                                   step="0.01" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Boş Ağırlık</label>
                            <input asp-for="Entity.EmptyQuantity"
                                   id="emptyQuantity"
                                   class="form-control"
                                   type="number"
                                   step="0.01" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Net Ağırlık</label>
                            <input type="number"
                                   asp-for="Entity.NetQuantity"
                                   id="netQuantity"
                                   class="form-control"
                                   step="0.01"
                                   readonly data-diff-a="filledQuantity" data-diff-b="emptyQuantity" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <label class="form-label">Açıklama</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="Entity.Description"
                                      rows="3"
                                      class="form-control"></textarea>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label">Kayıt Eden</label>
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-text">
                                    <ion-icon name="person-outline"></ion-icon>
                                </span>
                                <input class="form-control"
                                       value="@ViewBag.AppUserName"
                                       disabled />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Entity.DepartmentId" />
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Entity.AppUserId" />
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Entity.InsertDate" />
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Entity.UpdateDate" />

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="modal-footer">

                    <button type="button"
                            class="btn btn-light"
                            data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                        İptal
                    </button>

                    <button type="submit"
                            class="btn btn-success px-4">
                        <ion-icon name="save-outline"></ion-icon>
                        @(Model.IsEdit ? "Güncelle" : "Kaydet")
                    </button>

                </div>

            </form>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

